<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak breadcrumbs in milk for 15m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add ground beef, egg, parsley, pecorino cheese and orm into croquettes the size of lipstick]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sear the meatballs (dip in a deep frier if you have one) on high heat until seared, about 1m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[lower heat and cook gently]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[saute onion in olive oil until translucent, about 6m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add passata and onions to meatballs, cook on medium heat for 10m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[process almonds to a coarse powder]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add to meatballs and increase heat to high, until it starts boiling, about 1m]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
